    <div class="project-item project-currency-goals">
      <p>
        From using currency converter applications, free or paid, available on
        the App Store I found that these were either unnecessarily complex,
        unintuitive, or haven’t been updated new iPhone screen sizes. Very often
        these apps have a walkthrough to explain the complex interactions or
        features, when I thought they were meant to be simple.
      </p>
      <p>
        I designed Currency to be the simplest and most intuitive currency
        converter in the App Store, that would look perfect on any iPhone
        screen. My target customer is a traveller in a foreign country and the
        target moment is that traveller wanting to know the value of the foreign
        currency in their home currency.
      </p>
