      <p>
        The final design focuses on doing one job well: converting a foreign
        currency into the customer’s home currency. Features such as currency
        fluctuation graphs, in-app settings and notifications were not necessary
        for this job.
      </p>
      <p>
        One of the most unique aspects of Currency is the formatting of the
        currencies, with the correct symbol, correct number of decimal places,
        decimal divider and group dividers.
