        used country flags. One of the early designs uses a blue and dark visual
        style that I later on retired. While asking for feedback, friends seemed
        confused about which number they were editing so I added a text input
        blinking cursor.
      </p>
      <p>
        The final design is bright and shows activity indicators when the
        currency exchange rates are being updated. Other settings were added via
        the iOS Settings based on user feedback.
